*STORY*
once ypon a time in a forest hter live a monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on the bank of the river and in the same forest there live a crocodile and his wife.....
one day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree and the kind huted monkey offered him some fruits the crocodile came back the next day for  more fruits as he loved them .
as day past by the crocodile and the monkey became good friends
